    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子言：「不也，須菩提！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b06_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「乃至一切法、一切法真如，於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提可退轉不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b07_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子言：「不也，須菩提！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b08_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b09_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b09_27",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有法於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提可退轉者，是法即有所住。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b10_28",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以一切法無住，當有何法而可退轉？",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b11_29",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b12_30",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真如可退轉不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b12_31",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子言：「不也，須菩提！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b12_32",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b13_33",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是一切法實求不可得，即無法於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提可得退轉。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b13_34",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者舍利子白尊者須菩提言：「如尊者所說義，即無菩薩於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提有所退轉。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如是者，如佛所說，求三乘人應無差別耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者滿慈子語尊者舍利子言：「汝當問尊者須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如須菩提意，欲令唯有一乘人耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時，舍利子即如所說語尊者須菩提言：「汝須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲令唯有一乘人耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝於真如法中有一乘人而可見不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子言：「不也，須菩提！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「又，舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝於真如法中有三乘人而可見不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子言：「不也，須菩提！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "真如法中有一相三相而可得不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子言：「不也，須菩提！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今當知，真如法中，一菩薩法尚不可得，何況聲聞、緣覺之法而可得耶？",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640b29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故無有少法於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提有所退轉。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩聞作是說，不驚不怖不退失者，當知是菩薩摩訶薩即能成就菩提。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，世尊讚尊者須菩提言：「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝所樂說，皆是如來威神護念。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝所說，如是，如是！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩聞作是說，不驚不怖不退失者，當知是菩薩摩訶薩即能成就菩提。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者舍利子白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩聞作是說，不驚怖退失者，當得成就何等菩提？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「舍利子！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當得成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩欲得成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，應云何住？",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何修學？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩欲得成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，當於一切眾生起平等心、無毒心、慈心、利益心、善知識心、無障礙心、謙下心、無惱心、不害心，當生如是等心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又於一切眾生作父想、母想、諸親友想。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復長時廣修諸行，所謂於施能捨、於戒能護、於忍能受、精進無懈、禪定寂靜、智慧勝解。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "修如是等種種勝行，隨順緣生觀察諸法，不於諸法取斷滅相。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知諸法真實，即能過菩薩地具諸佛法，成熟無量無數有情，普令安住大涅盤界。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若如是修學，即無障礙相，乃至一切法亦得無障礙。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c27_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩摩訶薩欲得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，當如是住，如是修學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者，能為一切眾生作大依怙。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0640c28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說佛母出生三法藏般若波羅蜜多經卷第十五",
        "from": "T08n0228_015:0641a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]